---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Trophy, Users, Bike, Heart } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="Iván Castro | Lifestyle">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-pink-400 font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">Lifestyle</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Más allá del <span class="text-primary">Código</span>.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Equilibrio entre la vida profesional y personal. Lo que me mueve fuera de la terminal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 auto-rows-[300px] gap-4 md:gap-6">
        
        <div class="sm:col-span-2 sm:row-span-2 relative group overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-card border border-white/10">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-800">
                <img 
                  src="/img/ivan-running.jpeg" 
                  alt="Corriendo" 
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-40" 
                  onerror="this.style.display='none'" 
                />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 z-10 pointer-events-none">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/20">
                    <Trophy size={24} />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Running & Constancia</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                   La preparación de una <strong>Media Maratón</strong> me enseñó que los resultados llegan con disciplina diaria, no con sprints puntuales.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-card border border-white/10 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-pink-500/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 text-white/5 pointer-events-none">
                <Users size={140} />
            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <Users class="text-pink-400 mb-4" size={32} />
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Mi Equipo</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Tengo la suerte de contar con una gran familia y de un grupo de amigos que me aportan un entorno íncreíble.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-card border border-white/10">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-800">
                <img 
                  src="/img/ivan-running-friends.jpeg" 
                  alt="Amigos" 
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-80" 
                  onerror="this.style.display='none'" 
                />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:col-span-2 relative group overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-card border border-white/10">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-800">
                <img 
                  src="/img/ivan-family.png" 
                  alt="Familia" 
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-50" 
                  onerror="this.style.display='none'" 
                />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 z-10">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <Heart class="text-red-400 fill-red-400" size={24} />
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Familia</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm">
                   Desconexión y buenos momentos en los lugares de siempre.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:col-span-4 relative group overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-[#15181e] border border-white/10 h-[300px] sm:h-[350px]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-900">
                <img 
                    src="/img/ivan-bike.jpeg" 
                    alt="Ciclismo" 
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-40"
                    style="object-position: center 60%;" 
                    onerror="this.style.display='none'" 
                />
            </div>
            
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/80 via-black/40 to-transparent p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center items-start">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary border border-primary/20 backdrop-blur-md">
                    <Bike size={32} />
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                    Sobre dos ruedas
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
                    La bici es la forma de retarme a mí mismo, explorar nuevas rutas y limpiar la mente. Kilómetros, desnivel y libertad.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5">
            ← Volver al inicio
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>